  lines:
  - Oh, dear knight, you don't need to know who I am. Just think of me as a gracious
    soul blessing your way.
  - 'This are free of charge of course. If you choose to stay in here and see what
    more i can offer you, maybe you will discover some other things. '
  - 'Your first choice: The armor of a champion. With this armor, made of the scales
    and skin of a ferocious dragon, the monsters will barely harm you. With this,
    you won''t have to be injured and wounded like you were ever again. '
  - 'Your second choice: The gift of a fae, the regeneration of flesh. With this
    gift, you will recover instantly, your wounds will heal, the poison won''t affect
    your body and the sickness won''t take you. '
  - 'Your third choice: The blade of a legend. A sword that has never known defeat,
    carried by the greatest warriors of every age. With this in your hand, no enemy
    will stand before you, and your name will be spoken with fear and reverence.'
